Pour configurer le git sur un nouveau linux
sudo yum install git
git config --global user.name "brunoToukam"
git config --global user.email "brunotoukam@gmail.com"


information about begenning a project on git
first: write something in the README.md
second: git init
and then and for all add

git add README.md
git commit -m "commit name. exp first commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/brunoToukam/repository_name.git
git push -u origin master
